snippet.title: Sleight of Hand Trailer
snippet.description:
Infiltrate a hardboiled, rain-slicked city of taboo, where ritual magic and cursed artefacts set apart those with power from those without. Sleight of Hand is a 3rd-person Stealth-Action Deckbuilder about taking down the coven you used to run with.

Wishlist the game at:  stealth.game
